lead_paragraph: Queensland Reds have been dealt a heavy blow on the eve of the start of the Super Rugby season with flanker Liam Gill ruled out of the first month of the competition with a back injury.

headline.print_headline: Blow for Reds as Gill Ruled Out for Four Weeks
headline.main: Blow for Reds as Gill Ruled Out for Four Weeks
